{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_08_03",
  "title": "成宮すず 3話 私達のshiny",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――すずと芽衣がユニットバトルで優勝した、数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days after Suzu and Mei won the unit battle",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ここで新曲のジャケット写真を撮影するのですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re taking the jacket photo for the new song here‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1333331267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.7999997933
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "犬や猫が沢山いて\nとっっっっっても可愛い写真になりそうですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are so many dogs and cats here.\nIt’s going to be a suuuuper cute photo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4666666031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.56666646
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "……って、芽衣！？　まだ撮影は始まってないのに\n猫とじゃれあったらダメですわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Mei!? You can’t play with the cat\nbefore we start shooting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4666666031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ああもうっ、衣装が猫の毛まみれではありませんか\nこっちに来なさい。衣装に付いた毛を取ってあげますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ now yout outfit is covered in cat fur!\nCome here. I’ll get the fur off your outfit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7666666031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.8999997933
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、芽衣は私が面倒を見てあげないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ Mei‚ you’re so helpless without me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8999997933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.2051641111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "きゃあっ！　どうして私に抱きつくんですの！？\n離れなさい、私の衣装まで毛だらけにする気ですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaa! Why are you hugging me!?\nGet off me! Do you want to get fur all over my outfit too?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2051641111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "相変わらず二人は仲がいいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You two are still as close as ever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2333270232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2333288033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "仲良くなんてありませんわ！\n見てないで芽衣をなんとかしてくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re not close!\nDo something about Mei!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7481534882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.3666622798
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……撮影前からどっと疲れましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haah… I’m already exhausted‚ and we haven’t even started shooting yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4333267688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はまだ猫と遊んでいるようだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei seems to still be playing with the cat…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8333267688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.2666601021
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "好きにさせておけばいいのですわ\nもう止めるのも疲れました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just let her be.\nI’m too tired to stop her anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9666622798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "……それに、ああやって自由に楽しんでる方が\n芽衣はいい表情が出来ますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ she makes better expressions\nwhen she’s having fun like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.9666622798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.5999934355
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今日の撮影で本物の犬と猫を使いたいと提案したのは\nすずだそうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard that you were the one who suggested using real dogs and cats\nfor today’s shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.4517731271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "それは正確ではありませんわね\n正しくは、私と芽衣の二人で考えたのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not entirely accurate.\nTo be precise‚ Mei and I thought of it together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1999956131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.3333267688
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "どんなジャケット写真がいいか話していたら\n芽衣が突拍子もないことを言い出して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were discussing what kind of jacket photo we wanted‚\nand then Mei said something outrageous…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3999956131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "そのままではとても実現出来そうにないので\n私が実現可能な形に落とし込んで提案したのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It sounded impossible to actually do‚\nso I refined it into a feasible proposal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7333289464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.5999934355
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり芽衣には私が付いていないとダメですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei really needs me to look after her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.5999934355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.3666601021
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "二人の希望か……。それで思い出したが、前に\n新曲の構想について話してくれたことがあっただろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of your wishes‚ huh… That reminds me‚\nyou told me about your vision for the new song before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0666622798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "すずと芽衣の『大好き』を詰め込んだ曲にしたい\n……だったよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You wanted to make a song filled with the things you and Mei “love”…\nRight?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9666643143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.19999547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、芽衣と一緒に考えた歌詞には\n私達の大好きが詰まっているのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ the lyrics we came up with together‚ Mei‚\nare full of the things we love!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.533330981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに「すずしい顔してドーナツ Eating！」\nという歌詞があるが、これを考えたのはどっちなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ who came up with the line‚\n“Cool face‚ Donut Eating!”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.9999976476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.1333288033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "そこは芽衣ですわね。大好きなドーナツを\n歌詞に入れたいと芽衣が言い出したのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was Mei. She wanted to include donuts‚\nwhich she loves‚ in the lyrics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.3026834894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "「楽にfly me わけないメイビー」という歌詞は\nどっちが入れたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And which one of you put in the line‚\n“Take it easy‚ fly me‚ not so easy‚ Maybe”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.133330981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.7666621367
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "その歌詞は私が考えました。それが何か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I came up with that line. What about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.7666621367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、芽衣が考えた歌詞には『すず』が\nすずが考えた歌詞には『メイ』が入っていたからな",
      "translations": {
